find_library(_hdf5_hl_library
                 names hdf5_hl hdf5_serial_hl
                 hints ${_hdf5_library_search_dirs}
                 no_cmake_system_path)

find_library(pnetcdf_library
                             names pnetcdf
                             hints ${pnetcdf_dir}
                             path_suffixes "lib" "lib"
                             no_default_path)

find_library(faodel_library
        names tcmalloc spinlock sbl faodel-common whookie faodel-services nnti lunasa opbox dirman kelpie
        hints ${faodel_library_dir}
        no_default_path)

find_library(faodel_library
          names tcmalloc spinlock sbl faodel-common whookie faodel-services nnti lunasa opbox dirman kelpie
          hints ${faodel_dir} ${faodel_dir}/lib
          path_suffixes "lib" "lib"
          no_default_path)

find_library(faodel_library
        names tcmalloc spinlock sbl faodel-common whookie faodel-services nnti lunasa opbox dirman kelpie
        path_suffixes ${faodel_lib_suffixes})

find_library(cgns_library
                             names cgns
                             hints ${cgns_dir}
                             path_suffixes "lib" "lib"
                             no_default_path)

find_library(netcdf_c_library
                             names netcdf
                             hints ${netcdf_dir}
                             path_suffixes "lib" "lib"
                             no_default_path)

find_program(netcdf_config nc-config
                       paths ${netcdf_dir}/bin ${netcdf_bin_dir}
		           no_default_path
		           no_cmake_system_path
                       doc "netcdf configuration script")
